node.text: @ding_li_yong straw headed bulbul eggs correct or not?

Meanwhile at GUI, beautiful things are still happening! A while back one of our staff found these gorgeous pink eggs of a bulbul. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
We also have set up a cosy retail corner in the yuanqi 源启 (living room) space, offering fresh organic greens every Tue and Fri 2-4pm and Sat 10am-1pm! 🍄🍆🍌🥒 ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
We are especially grateful to a kind Carouseller who gifted us 
beautiful glass cabinets to display our dried produce in. If you're reading this, thank you so much! 💞🙆🏻‍♀️ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Truly if we open our eyes to the world we will soon find evidence that life goes on and rejuvenates itself, and that mother nature is still doing so much heavy lifting to feed us, and fill our spirits! We hope you are keeping well and find your moments of joy and wonder as we head into our final week of circuit breaker. 💛💛💛 ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Cheers,
Ground Up Initiative ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#GUICircuitBreaker #SGUnited #CircuitBreaker #StayHomeSG
